  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Agent Skills. The open standard for A I agent capabilities.",
      "checksum": "sha256:92a1354495b0ddb5e0beddb2b4cc086b5ab20ba83ff650ba2156cc93fc587534",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Built by Anthropic. Adopted by thirty-seven tools.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c81f48272cc76804e7ad6c252bc8f8fa65de94c62ab7292fb6a6da9fb8a616c0",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Here is how it works in under three minutes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af115f179a9c8f90f2fbe11bd41aea5574f514b7b91419f09c5aa236ae81e32f",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 17
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "A skill is one folder. Inside lives one file.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a7551a610a5ed878fb41b4a875486d84dc039922cd92d5bd5b3014ec9e1c6871",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 26
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Skill dot M D. That file holds two fields.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6654532173d1620265d551a9d0130eaeca94dedf86c20ca7e82280a84cf75bc4",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 35
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "A name. A description. Plus the instructions an agent follows to do the work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6dc891573f0f73759c2f5388db5b51667797a008da5e075c4e10684da7ef4bcd",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 44
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "That is the whole spec. A skill is more than just Skill dot M D though.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d36234cf978df2b7bb7a3efb578494aa8d4d6afffea249484bd8b4e3dc029209",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 58
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Drop scripts into a scripts folder, and the agent runs them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f310d4439867be2a8c44d254c60ecd7d45daf076513cbb010a82b8c9c71598d8",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 74
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Drop reference docs into a references folder, and the agent reads them on demand.",
      "checksum": "sha256:53bf650cae51e6c30205ed01902c3c79d01b6507ebfc872fc60166ed8bc37b02",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 85
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Drop templates into assets, and the agent uses them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f622ab60261c22202f2192a272bd0633ab0ef26a7f731a09a878870b211d0c85",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 99
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Here is the part that makes it actually work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bcc9a6b3e8aa561c966fe3b7fa36315e042020fa69bfbfec8a4e34c9b4281e33",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 108
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Progressive disclosure. Stage one. Discovery.",
      "checksum": "sha256:300726ce3ab257144327a5bdf851801c5018885d7a35afbfe866a79c1ff1f88c",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "At startup, the agent loads only each skill's name and description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2331d608908bbe4e6a46dd9267d83bbfcce36d9dfc297b84d184121da4984974",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 122
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "About a hundred tokens each. Stage two. Activation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:36380014db13b23d846b917796dff764f09d46129d6fbe54d5838822323d752e",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 133
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "When your task matches the description, the full Skill dot M D loads into context.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bb776b6508c096564c57149fd57bd1e247da174b49434f386686ba2558b507bd",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 141
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Stage three. Execution. Bundled scripts and reference files only load when the work demands them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b933f07f191fb2960f0f6d5a4323ab2b059cd06fa319c20b29e267b861a7fe76",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 5.572789115646258,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 156
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Skills stay small until you need them. This is what a real Skill dot M D looks like.",
      "checksum": "sha256:47f09081ba0a2b509ddd8b91af959a0a2c42d383eed93e536dde24f876885db8",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Required fields. A name. A description. Optional fields.",
      "checksum": "sha256:001784b1a3082eeada1773df8b2a6cc5977d7a0b33b3627ab6d0ea744906310c",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 189
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "A license. Compatibility hints. Metadata.",
      "checksum": "sha256:83a95cd80223622871480951fce80724746d1f550bd02d778b511aa7a0c79c8d",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 197
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Even pre-approved tools. Then Markdown instructions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3001552d97e74a0b7ee37dcf2fe28385f77d7d5d09edc771af7961f1e2a5a402",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 202
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "No D S L. No S D K. Just a file in your Git repo.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7b3d67ae95bb9b62dedc5cf15d1d08a4dcc9d376a5d6a61574839659bfc05f7d",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 208
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Here is the receipt. A hundred tokens to advertise a skill.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8df5ce73778049f26de348772aa999e6cc49f8ea5d3ca0d51edc476e40e333ae",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 223
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Five thousand tokens to run it. Zero tokens until activation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cff0bb88a56500edaaec6e2931219a339f5b87d4b7e8d6f0fc0a59ec47599d48",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 234
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Many skills. Tiny context footprint. So where can you use it?",
      "checksum": "sha256:d6a01a17d34ca894bc9a3a000276f1ac47418f86b644489ab144446114bc695a",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 244
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Claude Code. Cursor. V S Code. OpenAI Codex.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4364d792cf1a1abf7546c321c5b92fcacc6108d6d6d968d1753cc71665960ddf",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 255
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "And dozens more. Same file. Same format.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d60332b477b3fa79e4b03c92c3b55d746272a2146520b3aa9194de4f3ffd2524",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 263
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Zero rewrites. The format was originally developed by Anthropic.",
      "checksum": "sha256:203764880bae9b883caf80dc90cd441865e00997928892ed43fefd1b25940c6f",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 270
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Then released as an open standard. Open to contributions from anyone in the ecosystem.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a70ed29e88ac2e3ac8155e41f390d5186434acfd25fc089421168ccf51212eb7",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 279
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "So one question. Skills, or M C P? Which one earns the spot in your stack first?",
      "checksum": "sha256:620c5f328fa7895eb0757d850e763fef48a704818c52d69b68aab85182e37a67",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 293
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Drop your pick in the comments. Full spec at agentskills dot io.",
      "checksum": "sha256:953d859d12850e18c2d00e7064e0f04a9c5abd0bff33ce32c9c175e9d42fdf43",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 310
    }
  ]
}